ackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Amulet_of_restful_sleep/zh-CN\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Amulet_of_restful_sleep_zh-CN rootpage-Amulet_of_restful_sleep skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Amulet of restful sleep/zh-CN</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"><span class=\"subpages\">&lt; <a href=\"/wiki/Amulet_of_restful_sleep\" title=\"Amulet of restful sleep\">Amulet of restful sleep</a></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"width:50%;margin:auto;border:solid 3px #32CD32;background-color:#00FF00;text-align:center;clear:both\">\n<p><b>NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！</b><br />\n<a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN\" title=\"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\">了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"languages\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Amulet_of_restful_sleep\" title=\"Amulet of restful sleep\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"ko\"><a href=\"/wiki/Amulet_of_restful_sleep/ko\" title=\"Amulet of restful sleep/ko\">한국어</a></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin:0\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-cyan\">\"</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Circular_amulet.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Circular amulet.png\" src=\"/images/8/8b/Circular_amulet.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>深度睡眠护身符\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"随机外观 (page does not exist)\">随机</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>150 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid/zh-CN\" title=\"Zorkmid/zh-CN\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">20</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>深度睡眠护身符</b>（amulet of restful sleep）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%8A%A4%E8%BA%AB%E7%AC%A6\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"护身符\">护身符</a>。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.95.88.E6.9E.9C\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">效果</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#SLASH.27EM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SLASH'EM</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>随机生成的护身符有13.5%的概率是深度睡眠护身符。该护身符生成时有90.5%的概率为被诅咒的，9%的概率为未诅咒的，0.5%的概率为被祝福的。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"效果\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.95.88.E6.9E.9C\">效果</span></h2>\n<p>佩戴深度睡眠护身符会获得<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"深度睡眠 (page does not exist)\">深度睡眠</a>特质：玩家会在接下来的100回合之内的某个随机时间点陷入<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"睡眠 (page does not exist)\">睡眠</a>；睡着后，玩家会在1至20回合后醒来，或在被打扰时醒来。只要玩家持有深度睡眠特质，该现象就会周期性地发生。获得<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%97&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"睡眠抵抗 (page does not exist)\">睡眠抵抗</a>不会移除该效果，但可以使玩家不会睡着。\n</p>\n<div class=\"upcoming\">\n<p><i>以下内容涉及即将到来的版本（<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.7.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.7.0\">NetHack 3.7.0</a>）之信息。如果该版本已发布，请验证此处信息是否准确，并作出相应修改，以将其并入页面。</i>\n</p>\n当玩家因深度睡眠特质入睡时，其<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"生命值 (page does not exist)\">生命值</a>每回合额外回复1点，如同具有<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%86%8D%E7%94%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"再生 (page does not exist)\">再生</a>特质一般。若玩家未变形为其他怪物，该生命值回复效果能够和自然回复，以及其他来源（比如再生特质）的生命回复效果叠加。和再生特质不同的是，深度睡眠提供的回复效果不会加速饱腹度下降。</div>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>不要在前期随意佩戴未鉴定的护身符，如果你不幸戴上了被诅咒的深度睡眠护身符，你很可能会在睡着时受到怪物的袭击。\n</p><p>虽然并不推荐佩戴未鉴定的护身符，但深度睡眠护身符很容易通过佩戴来鉴定：只要你在佩戴未鉴定的护身符时会间歇性地睡着，而且没有受到睡眠攻击或<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%82%AC%E7%9C%A0%E6%B0%94%E4%BD%93%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"催眠气体陷阱 (page does not exist)\">催眠气体陷阱</a>的影响，那么这个护身符就是深度睡眠护身符。反之，如果你没有睡眠抗性且在100回合内从未睡着过，那这个护身符一定是其他类别。\n</p><p>在实际应用场景，推荐将该护身符保留起来用于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"批量变形 (page does not exist)\">批量变形</a>以获得更好的护身符。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>深度睡眠护身符最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.0.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.0.0\">NetHack 3.0.0</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Amulet_of_restful_sleep/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span id=\"SLASH'EM\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SLASH.27EM\">SLASH'EM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SLASH%27EM\" title=\"SLASH&#39;EM\">SLASH'EM</a>, putting on a <a href=\"/wiki/Blessed\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Blessed\">blessed</a> amulet of restful sleep will put you to sleep immediately, allowing you to specify for how long (up to 500 turns); the sleep cycle will then continue as in vanilla <i>NetHack</i>. Sleeping slows down <a href=\"/wiki/Nutrition\" title=\"Nutrition\">nutrition</a> burn as well in SLASH'EM, giving the amulet some marginal use if you don't have a <a href=\"/wiki/Ring_of_slow_digestion\" title=\"Ring of slow digestion\">ring of slow digestion</a>.\n</p>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182301\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.033 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.071 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 248/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1109/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4233/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 685/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   42.975      1 -total\n 31.66%   13.606      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 26.07%   11.205      1 Template:Languages\n 25.97%   11.161      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n 18.21%    7.824      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 15.89%    6.827      1 Template:Amulet/zh-CN\n 14.28%    6.137      1 Template:Top_icon\n  6.67%    2.865      1 Template:Needhelp/zh-CN\n  6.35%    2.727      1 Template:Upcoming/zh-CN\n  5.18%    2.224      1 Template:Cnlink\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:39189-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926182301 and revision id 163577\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Amulet_of_restful_sleep/zh-CN&amp;oldid=163577\">https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Amulet_of_restful_sleep/zh-CN&amp;oldid=163577</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Upcoming\" title=\"Category:Upcoming\">